specJson.name: brightics.function.extraction$capitalize_variable
specJson.description:
This function returns a copy of the string in which all characters have been replaced by capitalized/uncapitalized characters.

References:
+ <https://www.tutorialspoint.com/python/string_upper.htm>
+ <https://www.tutorialspoint.com/python/string_lower.htm>
+ <https://www.programiz.com/python-programming/methods/string/upper>
+ <https://www.programiz.com/python-programming/methods/string/lower>

out_table.desc: Output table with the capitalized/uncapitalized results.

params.label: Suffix of Out Column Name
params.description: Suffix of the newly generated columns (default = _upper for Uppercase mode, _lower for Lowercase mode).

summary.en: Capitalized/uncapitalize all characters in string variables
summary.ko: 문자열 변수의 모든 문자를 대문자/소문자로 변환합니다.

md.en:
# Capitalize Variable Capitalized/uncapitalize all characters in string variables. ## Description Returns a copy of the string in which all characters have been replaced by capitalized/uncapitalized characters. References: + + + + ## Properties ### VA #### INPUT 1. **table***: (Table) Input table. #### OUTPUT 1. **out_table**: (Table) Output table with the capitalized/uncapitalized results. #### PARAMETER 1. **Input Columns***: String columns to be capitalized/uncapitalized. 2. **Replace Mode**: Uppercase / Lowercase (default = Uppercase) 3. **Suffix of Out Column Name**: Suffix of the newly generated columns (default = _upper for Uppercase mode, _lower for Lowercase mode). ### Python #### USAGE ``` capitalize_variable(table = , input_cols = , replace = , out_col_suffix = ) ``` #### INPUT 1. **table***: (Table) Input table. #### OUTPUT 1. **out_table**: (Table) Output table with the capitalized/uncapitalized results. #### PARAMETER 1. **input_cols***: String columns to be capitalized/uncapitalized. * Type: *list[str]* 2. **replace**: Uppercase / Lowercase (default = Uppercase) * Type: *str* * Default / Range: upper ( upper | lower ) 3. **out_col_suffix**: Suffix of the newly generated columns (default = _upper for Uppercase mode, _lower for Lowercase mode). * Type: *str* ## Example ### VA **[Sample Model]**
In this tutorial workflow, strings in the 'species' column in sample_iris data is capitalized. ++Parameters++ 1. **Input Columns***: species 2. **Replace Mode**: Uppercase 3. **Suffix of Out Column Name**: '_upper' ### Python ``` from brightics.function.extraction import capitalize_variable res = capitalize_variable(table=inputs[0], input_cols=['species'], replace='upper', out_col_suffix='_upper') table = res['out_table'] ```
In this python script, strings in the 'species' column in sample_iris data is capitalized.
md.kr:
# 대/소문자 변환 문자열의 모든 문자들을 대문자/소문자로 변환한다. ## Description 모든 문자가 대문자/소문자로 변환된 문자열의 복사본을 반환한다. References: + + + + ## Properties ### VA #### INPUT 1. **table***: (Table) 입력 테이블. #### OUTPUT 1. **out_table**: (Table) 대문자/소문자로 변환된 결과 테이블. #### PARAMETER 1. **Input Columns***: 대문자/소문자로 변환할 컬럼. 2. **Replace Mode**: Uppercase / Lowercase (default = Uppercase) 3. **Suffix of Out Column Name**: 새로 생성된 컬럼의 접미사 (default = _upper for Uppercase mode, _lower for Lowercase mode). ### Python #### USAGE ``` capitalize_variable(table = , input_cols = , replace = , out_col_suffix = ) ``` #### INPUT 1. **table***: (Table) 입력 테이블. #### OUTPUT 1. **out_table**: (Table) 대문자/소문자로 변환된 결과 테이블. #### PARAMETER 1. **input_cols***: 대문자/소문자로 변환할 컬럼. * Type: *list[str]* 2. **replace**: Uppercase / Lowercase (default = Uppercase) * Type: *str* * Default / Range: upper ( upper | lower ) 3. **out_col_suffix**: 새로 생성된 컬럼의 접미사 (default = _upper for Uppercase mode, _lower for Lowercase mode). * Type: *str* ## Example ### VA **[Sample Model]**
이 튜토리얼 워크플로우에서, sample_iris 데이터의 'species' 컬럼에 있는 문자열들이 대문자로 변환된다. ++Parameters++ 1. **Input Columns***: species 2. **Replace Mode**: Uppercase 3. **Suffix of Out Column Name**: '_upper' ### Python ``` from brightics.function.extraction import capitalize_variable res = capitalize_variable(table=inputs[0], input_cols=['species'], replace='upper', out_col_suffix='_upper') table = res['out_table'] ```
이 파이썬 스크립트에서, sample_iris 데이터의 'species' 컬럼에 있는 문자열들이 대문자로 변환된다.
